"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president warned after Iran attacked near an Israeli nuclear facility. Tehran said one of its nuclear sites was targeted. The head of the International Atomic Energy Agency asked for military restraint after the attacks.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Warns After Iran Attack\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. advirti\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de que Ir\u00e1n atac\u00f3 cerca de una instalaci\u00f3n nuclear israel\u00ed. Teher\u00e1n dijo que uno de sus sitios nucleares fue atacado. El jefe de la Agencia Internacional de Energ\u00eda At\u00f3mica pidi\u00f3 moderaci\u00f3n militar despu\u00e9s de los ataques.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. advierte tras ataque de Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Hawaii Governor Josh Green warned people not to take the storm lightly as more rain is expected on Oahu and Maui.\",            \"english_title\": \"Hawaii Governor Warns About Storm\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobernador de Haw\u00e1i, Josh Green, advirti\u00f3 a la gente que no tome la tormenta a la ligera ya que se espera m\u00e1s lluvia en Oahu y Maui.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Gobernador de Haw\u00e1i advierte sobre tormenta\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Statements from President Trump saying the war is almost over do not match the reality on the ground.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump's War Statements Questioned\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las declaraciones del presidente Trump diciendo que la guerra casi termina no coinciden con la realidad en el terreno.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Declaraciones de guerra de Trump cuestionadas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two children, aged 11 and 15, were injured in an attack in Zaporizhzhia.\",            \"english_title\": \"Children Injured in Zaporizhzhia Attack\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos ni\u00f1os, de 11 y 15 a\u00f1os, resultaron heridos en un ataque en Zaporizhzhia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ni\u00f1os heridos en ataque en Zaporizhzhia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The president said ICE would handle security as airport security staff have not been paid for weeks due to a partial government shutdown.\",            \"english_title\": \"ICE to Handle Security Amid Shutdown\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente dijo que ICE se encargar\u00e1 de la seguridad ya que el personal de seguridad del aeropuerto no ha sido pagado durante semanas debido a un cierre parcial del gobierno.\",            \"translated_title\": \"ICE manejar\u00e1 seguridad durante cierre\"        }    ]}"